								Common Mistake
							</p>
							<p class="mt-1 text-muted-foreground">
								Fretting over whether you ate protein 30 minutes versus 90 minutes after a workout while ignoring that you only ate 80 g of protein all day is misplaced effort. Prioritize the daily total before optimizing timing.
